<h2>New Account Created</h2>

<p>A new user account has been created in the [% site_name || 'Comserv' %] system with the following details:</p>

<ul>
    <li><strong>Username:</strong> [% username %]</li>
    <li><strong>Name:</strong> [% first_name %] [% last_name %]</li>
    <li><strong>Email:</strong> [% email %]</li>
    <li><strong>Role(s):</strong> [% roles %]</li>
    <li><strong>Created at:</strong> [% created_at %]</li>
    [% IF mailing_lists && mailing_lists.size > 0 %]
    <li><strong>Mailing List Subscriptions:</strong>
        <ul>
            [% FOREACH list_name IN mailing_lists %]
            <li>[% list_name | html %]</li>
            [% END %]
        </ul>
    </li>
    [% ELSE %]
    <li><strong>Mailing List Subscriptions:</strong> None selected</li>
    [% END %]
</ul>

<p>This is an automated notification. No action is required.</p>